      <title>共和党在内华达州邮寄选票迟到问题上败下阵来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/republicans-lose-fight-over-late-arriving-mail-ballots-in-nevada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[内华达州最高法院将允许州官员计算 11 月 5 日大选后三天内到达的没有邮戳的缺席选票，驳回了摇摆州共和党提出的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/republicans-lose-fight-over-late-arriving-mail-ballots-in-nevada</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 17:04:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄勒冈州和华盛顿州的投票箱发生火灾，数百张选票被毁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-28/hundreds-of-ballots-are-destroyed-after-fires-are-set-in-ballot-drop-boxes-in-oregon-and-washington</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西雅图（美联社）——周一凌晨，俄勒冈州波特兰市和附近的华盛顿州温哥华市的投票箱发生火灾，数百张选票被毁，当局正在调查此事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-10-28/hundreds-of-ballots-are-destroyed-after-fires-are-set-in-ballot-drop-boxes-in-oregon-and-washington</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 16:53:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>取消富人税收减免为波多黎各竞选提供更多支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/ending-tax-breaks-for-wealthy-fuels-support-in-puerto-rico-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波多黎各州长竞选中，第三党候选人胡安·达尔毛 (Juan Dalmau) 的支持率飙升至几乎打成平手，因为他承诺终止针对该岛富裕新移民的税收减免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/ending-tax-breaks-for-wealthy-fuels-support-in-puerto-rico-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 16:42:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈马斯领导人被杀后以色列愿意在加沙短暂停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/israel-hamas-war-netanyahu-open-to-short-truce-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡表示，他愿意在以色列与哈马斯的战争中实现短暂停火，以便释放目前仍被伊朗支持的加沙激进组织扣押的约 100 名人质中的少数人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/israel-hamas-war-netanyahu-open-to-short-truce-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 16:22:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丰业银行经济学家称特朗普将带来“毁灭性”政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/scotiabank-economist-derek-holt-says-trump-would-bring-ruinous-economic-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位加拿大顶级经济学家警告说，唐纳德·特朗普的第二任总统任期可能会带来极端的保护主义、巨大的人口负面冲击以及大量债务发行，以资助“完全不受约束的财政政策”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/scotiabank-economist-derek-holt-says-trump-would-bring-ruinous-economic-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 15:47:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非就以色列种族灭绝案提交证据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/south-africa-files-evidence-in-israel-genocide-case-at-icj</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非周一向国际法院提交了一份卷宗，其中包含所谓的“事实和证据”，以证实以色列在加沙地带犯下种族灭绝罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/south-africa-files-evidence-in-israel-genocide-case-at-icj</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 15:36:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登批评马斯克赠送 100 万美元，提前投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/harris-trump-fan-out-to-swing-states-musk-sued-over-giveaways</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登称埃隆·马斯克向选定的登记选民提供 100 万美元作为选举抽奖的一部分的计划“不合适”，并对唐纳德·特朗普最著名的支持者之一激励选民的有争议的努力作出了回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/harris-trump-fan-out-to-swing-states-musk-sued-over-giveaways</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 15:31:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克因向选举机构提供 100 万美元赠款在宾夕法尼亚州遭起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/elon-musk-sued-over-1-million-election-giveaway-in-philadelphia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克因他所在的政治行动委员会在美国总统大选的最后几天针对摇摆州选民每天举办 100 万美元的抽奖活动而被费城地方检察官起诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/elon-musk-sued-over-1-million-election-giveaway-in-philadelphia</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 15:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列内阁改变会议地点，伊朗考虑回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/israeli-cabinet-meets-in-secret-location-after-iranian-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在伊朗表示将以相应方式回应以色列周六对其导弹和防空系统的袭击后，以色列政府将其例行会议转移到一个未公开的地点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/israeli-cabinet-meets-in-secret-location-after-iranian-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 14:01:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多竞争对手将取消对许多新建住宅征收联邦销售税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/trudeau-rival-pledges-to-axe-federal-sales-tax-on-many-new-homes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党领袖皮埃尔·波利耶夫 (Pierre Poilievre) 表示，如果他当选总理，他将取消加拿大针对售价低于 100 万加元（719,700 美元）的新房征收的 5% 的全国销售税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/trudeau-rival-pledges-to-axe-federal-sales-tax-on-many-new-homes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 12:18:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
